uneven rocky rise, a circle of standing stones watches the cold southern
coast in all the glory with which it was intended.  Curved, wide seams of
gleaming black are tightly held in stark contrast to the bright grey
stones, perfectly aligned about a central slab and with no apparent ruin. 
Grass grows abundantly...  life harmoniously surrounding, rather than
conquering, the stoic remnants of past knowledge.
